Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Kagome Higurashi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Born into an old and respected\nfamily of shrine keepers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a third-yearstudent in\nmiddle school living a normal life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But on my 15th birthday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was dragged into the\NFeudal Era{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by a demon who suddenly\nappeared from the shrine well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I met\nthe half-demon, Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:04.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shikon Jewel is a treasure which\nincreases the powerof a demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In orderto help Inuyasha\nand some others{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}find the shards of\nthe shattered Shikon Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:17.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been going back and forth between\nthe real world and the feudal period.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:26.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's a greedy one trying to get\nthe Shikon Jewel for himself... Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scheming to absorb the demon powers\nof Sesshomaru, Inuyasha's olderbrother,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku lures Sesshomaru to his castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And just as Naraku was about to\ncompletely consume Sesshomaru's body,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha broke through Naraku's barrier\nand rushed into the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:46.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!\NWind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My barrier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:53.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha was ready to deliver\nthe finishing blow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think you can escape\nfrom me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku used Sango's youngerbrother,\NKohaku, in a dastardly trick{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to make his escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't plan to return\nto this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:38.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afteryou broke through his barrier,\nhe had no choice but to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:46.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is probably vulnerable enough\nto be killed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if coming home\nwas the right thing to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm spending my time studying\nin this safe world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel bad about leaving\NInuyasha and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonderwhat they're doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This formula will appear in\nthe test two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rememberit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Test?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't be worrying about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to catch up\nin two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll end up flunking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, are you ready to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me\nborrow yournotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to study for\nthe test, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust want to borrow it\nfor a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Kagome, we know you're\nsickly and it's hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! So please help me out.\nljust want to make a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.\NI guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll lend you my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're thinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- About what?\N- Whatelse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourjealous, delinquent boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not! I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So how's itgoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the latest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I recently met his olderbrother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he also a delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he strong, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he may be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The two of them only argue\nwhen they see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's very dangerous.\NReally, really dangerous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we keep quiet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can just see it...\nherunhappy future!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where there's love,\nthere's hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there, Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What's the matter?\N- N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I borrow yournotes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:38.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's exam week in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all have the same plan\nas you, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?\NStand in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can make copies\nsomewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fast and easy copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,OUT OF ORDER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,CLOSED FORTHE DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,CLOSED FORTHE DAY\NSomewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Well, Kagome.\NWe have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's late! Kagome's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought she was returning\nright away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said she'd stay over\ntwo or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be impatient, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you stay so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like we only started\nhunting down Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd betterrest yourbody, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Sango?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not like you humans.\NI'm not a bit tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's just it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't keep up with\nyourenergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who's tired.\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's demonic aura\nremains hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've had my Soul Collectors\nlook fortraces of him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's not even a hint\nof his barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How has he hidden such\na strong demonic aura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get the Sacred Jewel shard\nfrom Kohaku's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to think this kid was\njust a puppet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he didn't kill the hostage girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nordid he allow himself to be\nkilled by Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, if you keep defying\NNaraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I shouldn't be\none to talk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Kohaku along with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... Miroku went to\nwoo Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:51.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome even suggested that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango's been secretly waiting\nforthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara...\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be worried about\nyourbrother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's easier said than done,\nbut don't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand what you're\ngoing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to be alone,\nafter all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, considering the\nway you usually are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought aftergiving me\nthe pep talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'd do something lecherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should have told me sooner\nif that's what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! Everyone's crazy\naround here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess there's no other way\nbut to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You ask someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right. 'Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Now why did I\ncall herin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, your textbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't do a thing last night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sis...\N- Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forgeteverything\NI memorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to catch up today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's here... Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late, so I came\nto get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a test tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen!\NDo NOTgo outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay put in the house\nand wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be back this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She forgot herlunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you take it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I follow Kagome's scent,\NI'll catch up to herright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone! Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, move outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's world is\npretty dangerous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NC'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:37.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man! What a dangerous world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! What's Inuyasha doing here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, Higurashi,\nyou can stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why'd she do this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I make it clear that\nyou were to stay home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!\NYourma asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He came to bring\nthis to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's share.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all squished to one side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be able to\nconcentrate at home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stay in the library\nuntil evening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to study!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is yourneuralgia cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're still young, so you\nmust take care of yourbody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I made up this healthy menu\nforyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo is so meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't I think of it earlier?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can ask Hojo forthe notes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hojo, wait up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is herbal medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it's supposed to work\non all kinds of ailments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, Higurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Health is a matter\nof the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:35.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Live a wholesome life,\neat three meals daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi, eat properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't borrow any notes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:01.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A strange-looking youth\nin a red outfit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}captured a bank robber.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this story about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}this youth rescued a child\ntrapped in a fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here is a drawing of his likeness\ndone by the rescued child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, that's the cap I was wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you do on the\nway to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, what's this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep Inuyasha company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let's take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's sooo hot!\NWhat is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon, you have to rinse\noff the suds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no...\NI've forgotten everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What IS this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My tongue is burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gave him curry.\NI guess it was too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This coming from a guy that normally\ngrins and bears a hole in his gut...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?\NI'm being quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's disconcerting to\nbe stared at.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get back\nto your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're goin' back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he intend to watch over\nme all night?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:41.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't put it past him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a fireball of energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-He's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez! What a guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Afterbothering me with my studies\nall this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've neverseen Inuyasha\nsleeping so soundly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's more exhausted\nthan any one of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sleep peacefully...\nat least on this night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, they're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you spent the night\nat Kagome's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kagome?\NYou have no energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You monopolized my bed\nlast night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of which,\nthe test was a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the pits!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a clear day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:49.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides the ones Naraku\nhas in his possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who has Sacred Jewel shards\nand how many?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:56.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Kohaku has one.\NKagome has three.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:58.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:23:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga of the Wolf-Demon Tribe\nhas one in each leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means Naraku will\ngo after Koga, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:06.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, Naraku has\ndisappeared from sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:07.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.22,0:24:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Female Wolf-Demon\nand the Lunar Rainbow Promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afemale wolf-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Koga is quite\nthe ladies' man!
